        <link href="https://lis-r-barreto.github.io/portfolio/blog/create-portfolio-with-github-pages-and-docusaurus"/>
        <updated>2024-11-20T00:00:00.000Z</updated>
        <summary type="html"><![CDATA[Aprenda como criar um portfólio profissional usando GitHub Pages e Docusaurus, passo a passo.]]></summary>
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>Criar um portfólio profissional pode ser fácil e acessível utilizando <strong>GitHub Pages</strong> e <strong>Docusaurus</strong>. Este guia irá te orientar passo a passo na configuração, personalização e publicação do seu portfólio.</p>
<hr>
<h2 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_LWe7" id="step-1-configure-o-ssh-com-github">Step 1: Configure o SSH com GitHub<a href="https://lis-r-barreto.github.io/portfolio/blog/create-portfolio-with-github-pages-and-docusaurus#step-1-configure-o-ssh-com-github" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to Step 1: Configure o SSH com GitHub" title="Direct link to Step 1: Configure o SSH com GitHub">​</a></h2>
<ol>
<li>
<p><strong>Gere uma nova chave SSH</strong>:</p>
<div class="language-bash codeBlockContainer_Ckt0 theme-code-block" style="--prism-color:#393A34;--prism-background-color:#f6f8fa"><div class="codeBlockContent_biex"><pre tabindex="0" class="prism-code language-bash codeBlock_bY9V thin-scrollbar" style="color:#393A34;background-color:#f6f8fa"><code class="codeBlockLines_e6Vv"><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">ssh-keygen -t ed25519 -C "seu_email@example.com"</span><br></span></code></pre><div class="buttonGroup__atx"><button type="button" aria-label="Copy code to clipboard" title="Copy" class="clean-btn"><span class="copyButtonIcons_eSgA" aria-hidden="true"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="copyButtonIcon_y97N"><path fill="currentColor" d="M19,21H8V7H19M19,5H8A2,2 0 0,0 6,7V21A2,2 0 0,0 8,23H19A2,2 0 0,0 21,21V7A2,2 0 0,0 19,5M16,1H4A2,2 0 0,0 2,3V17H4V3H16V1Z"></path></svg><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="copyButtonSuccessIcon_LjdS"><path fill="currentColor" d="M21,7L9,19L3.5,13.5L4.91,12.09L9,16.17L19.59,5.59L21,7Z"></path></svg></span></button></div></div></div>
</li>
<li>
<p><strong>Copie a chave SSH</strong> para o clipboard:</p>
<div class="language-bash codeBlockContainer_Ckt0 theme-code-block" style="--prism-color:#393A34;--prism-background-color:#f6f8fa"><div class="codeBlockContent_biex"><pre tabindex="0" class="prism-code language-bash codeBlock_bY9V thin-scrollbar" style="color:#393A34;background-color:#f6f8fa"><code class="codeBlockLines_e6Vv"><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">cat ~/.ssh/id_ed25519.pub</span><br></span></code></pre><div class="buttonGroup__atx"><button type="button" aria-label="Copy code to clipboard" title="Copy" class="clean-btn"><span class="copyButtonIcons_eSgA" aria-hidden="true"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="copyButtonIcon_y97N"><path fill="currentColor" d="M19,21H8V7H19M19,5H8A2,2 0 0,0 6,7V21A2,2 0 0,0 8,23H19A2,2 0 0,0 21,21V7A2,2 0 0,0 19,5M16,1H4A2,2 0 0,0 2,3V17H4V3H16V1Z"></path></svg><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="copyButtonSuccessIcon_LjdS"><path fill="currentColor" d="M21,7L9,19L3.5,13.5L4.91,12.09L9,16.17L19.59,5.59L21,7Z"></path></svg></span></button></div></div></div>
</li>
<li>
<p><strong>Adicione a chave SSH</strong> à sua conta do GitHub em <a href="https://github.com/settings/keys" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Configurações de SSH no GitHub</a>.</p>
</li>
</ol>
<hr>
<h2 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_LWe7" id="step-2-instale-nodejs-e-yarn-no-seu-computador">Step 2: Instale Node.js e Yarn no seu computador<a href="https://lis-r-barreto.github.io/portfolio/blog/create-portfolio-with-github-pages-and-docusaurus#step-2-instale-nodejs-e-yarn-no-seu-computador" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to Step 2: Instale Node.js e Yarn no seu computador" title="Direct link to Step 2: Instale Node.js e Yarn no seu computador">​</a></h2>
<p>Para instalar o <strong>Node.js</strong> e o <strong>Yarn</strong>, utilize o <strong>Node Version Manager (nvm)</strong>:</p>
<div class="language-bash codeBlockContainer_Ckt0 theme-code-block" style="--prism-color:#393A34;--prism-background-color:#f6f8fa"><div class="codeBlockContent_biex"><pre tabindex="0" class="prism-code language-bash codeBlock_bY9V thin-scrollbar" style="color:#393A34;background-color:#f6f8fa"><code class="codeBlockLines_e6Vv"><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain"># Instale o nvm</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">curl -o- https://raw.githubusercontent.com/nvm-sh/nvm/v0.39.7/install.sh | bash</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain" style="display:inline-block"></span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain"># Reinicie o terminal e instale o Node.js</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">nvm install 20</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain" style="display:inline-block"></span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain"># Verifique se o Node.js foi instalado corretamente</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">node -v # Deve exibir a versão 20.x</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain" style="display:inline-block"></span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain"># Instale o Yarn globalmente</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">npm install --global yarn</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">yarn --version</span><br></span></code></pre><div class="buttonGroup__atx"><button type="button" aria-label="Copy code to clipboard" title="Copy" class="clean-btn"><span class="copyButtonIcons_eSgA" aria-hidden="true"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="copyButtonIcon_y97N"><path fill="currentColor" d="M19,21H8V7H19M19,5H8A2,2 0 0,0 6,7V21A2,2 0 0,0 8,23H19A2,2 0 0,0 21,21V7A2,2 0 0,0 19,5M16,1H4A2,2 0 0,0 2,3V17H4V3H16V1Z"></path></svg><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="copyButtonSuccessIcon_LjdS"><path fill="currentColor" d="M21,7L9,19L3.5,13.5L4.91,12.09L9,16.17L19.59,5.59L21,7Z"></path></svg></span></button></div></div></div>
<hr>
<h2 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_LWe7" id="step-3-crie-um-repositório-no-github">Step 3: Crie um Repositório no GitHub<a href="https://lis-r-barreto.github.io/portfolio/blog/create-portfolio-with-github-pages-and-docusaurus#step-3-crie-um-reposit%C3%B3rio-no-github" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to Step 3: Crie um Repositório no GitHub" title="Direct link to Step 3: Crie um Repositório no GitHub">​</a></h2>
<p>Crie um novo repositório no GitHub com o nome desejado (exemplo: <code>portfolio</code>). Ele será usado para hospedar seu site.</p>
<hr>
<h2 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_LWe7" id="step-4-inicialize-um-projeto-docusaurus">Step 4: Inicialize um Projeto Docusaurus<a href="https://lis-r-barreto.github.io/portfolio/blog/create-portfolio-with-github-pages-and-docusaurus#step-4-inicialize-um-projeto-docusaurus" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to Step 4: Inicialize um Projeto Docusaurus" title="Direct link to Step 4: Inicialize um Projeto Docusaurus">​</a></h2>
<p>Crie um novo site com o comando:</p>
<div class="language-bash codeBlockContainer_Ckt0 theme-code-block" style="--prism-color:#393A34;--prism-background-color:#f6f8fa"><div class="codeBlockContent_biex"><pre tabindex="0" class="prism-code language-bash codeBlock_bY9V thin-scrollbar" style="color:#393A34;background-color:#f6f8fa"><code class="codeBlockLines_e6Vv"><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">npx create-docusaurus@latest portfolio classic --javascript</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">cd portfolio</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">yarn install</span><br></span></code></pre><div class="buttonGroup__atx"><button type="button" aria-label="Copy code to clipboard" title="Copy" class="clean-btn"><span class="copyButtonIcons_eSgA" aria-hidden="true"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="copyButtonIcon_y97N"><path fill="currentColor" d="M19,21H8V7H19M19,5H8A2,2 0 0,0 6,7V21A2,2 0 0,0 8,23H19A2,2 0 0,0 21,21V7A2,2 0 0,0 19,5M16,1H4A2,2 0 0,0 2,3V17H4V3H16V1Z"></path></svg><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="copyButtonSuccessIcon_LjdS"><path fill="currentColor" d="M21,7L9,19L3.5,13.5L4.91,12.09L9,16.17L19.59,5.59L21,7Z"></path></svg></span></button></div></div></div>
<p>Isso cria um site Docusaurus básico, que você pode personalizar.</p>
<hr>
<h2 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_LWe7" id="step-5-inicie-o-servidor-de-desenvolvimento">Step 5: Inicie o Servidor de Desenvolvimento<a href="https://lis-r-barreto.github.io/portfolio/blog/create-portfolio-with-github-pages-and-docusaurus#step-5-inicie-o-servidor-de-desenvolvimento" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to Step 5: Inicie o Servidor de Desenvolvimento" title="Direct link to Step 5: Inicie o Servidor de Desenvolvimento">​</a></h2>
<p>Para visualizar o site localmente, execute:</p>
<div class="language-bash codeBlockContainer_Ckt0 theme-code-block" style="--prism-color:#393A34;--prism-background-color:#f6f8fa"><div class="codeBlockContent_biex"><pre tabindex="0" class="prism-code language-bash codeBlock_bY9V thin-scrollbar" style="color:#393A34;background-color:#f6f8fa"><code class="codeBlockLines_e6Vv"><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">yarn start</span><br></span></code></pre><div class="buttonGroup__atx"><button type="button" aria-label="Copy code to clipboard" title="Copy" class="clean-btn"><span class="copyButtonIcons_eSgA" aria-hidden="true"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="copyButtonIcon_y97N"><path fill="currentColor" d="M19,21H8V7H19M19,5H8A2,2 0 0,0 6,7V21A2,2 0 0,0 8,23H19A2,2 0 0,0 21,21V7A2,2 0 0,0 19,5M16,1H4A2,2 0 0,0 2,3V17H4V3H16V1Z"></path></svg><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="copyButtonSuccessIcon_LjdS"><path fill="currentColor" d="M21,7L9,19L3.5,13.5L4.91,12.09L9,16.17L19.59,5.59L21,7Z"></path></svg></span></button></div></div></div>
<p>Acesse <code>http://localhost:3000</code> para visualizar seu site. Agora você pode personalizar o conteúdo.</p>
<hr>
<h2 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_LWe7" id="step-6-configure-o-git-e-envie-o-projeto-para-o-github">Step 6: Configure o Git e Envie o Projeto para o GitHub<a href="https://lis-r-barreto.github.io/portfolio/blog/create-portfolio-with-github-pages-and-docusaurus#step-6-configure-o-git-e-envie-o-projeto-para-o-github" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to Step 6: Configure o Git e Envie o Projeto para o GitHub" title="Direct link to Step 6: Configure o Git e Envie o Projeto para o GitHub">​</a></h2>
<ol>
<li>
<p>Inicialize o repositório Git:</p>
<div class="language-bash codeBlockContainer_Ckt0 theme-code-block" style="--prism-color:#393A34;--prism-background-color:#f6f8fa"><div class="codeBlockContent_biex"><pre tabindex="0" class="prism-code language-bash codeBlock_bY9V thin-scrollbar" style="color:#393A34;background-color:#f6f8fa"><code class="codeBlockLines_e6Vv"><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">git init</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">git status</span><br></span></code></pre><div class="buttonGroup__atx"><button type="button" aria-label="Copy code to clipboard" title="Copy" class="clean-btn"><span class="copyButtonIcons_eSgA" aria-hidden="true"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="copyButtonIcon_y97N"><path fill="currentColor" d="M19,21H8V7H19M19,5H8A2,2 0 0,0 6,7V21A2,2 0 0,0 8,23H19A2,2 0 0,0 21,21V7A2,2 0 0,0 19,5M16,1H4A2,2 0 0,0 2,3V17H4V3H16V1Z"></path></svg><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="copyButtonSuccessIcon_LjdS"><path fill="currentColor" d="M21,7L9,19L3.5,13.5L4.91,12.09L9,16.17L19.59,5.59L21,7Z"></path></svg></span></button></div></div></div>
</li>
<li>
<p>Adicione e faça o commit dos arquivos:</p>
<div class="language-bash codeBlockContainer_Ckt0 theme-code-block" style="--prism-color:#393A34;--prism-background-color:#f6f8fa"><div class="codeBlockContent_biex"><pre tabindex="0" class="prism-code language-bash codeBlock_bY9V thin-scrollbar" style="color:#393A34;background-color:#f6f8fa"><code class="codeBlockLines_e6Vv"><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">git add .</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">git commit -m "Initial commit for Docusaurus site"</span><br></span></code></pre><div class="buttonGroup__atx"><button type="button" aria-label="Copy code to clipboard" title="Copy" class="clean-btn"><span class="copyButtonIcons_eSgA" aria-hidden="true"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="copyButtonIcon_y97N"><path fill="currentColor" d="M19,21H8V7H19M19,5H8A2,2 0 0,0 6,7V21A2,2 0 0,0 8,23H19A2,2 0 0,0 21,21V7A2,2 0 0,0 19,5M16,1H4A2,2 0 0,0 2,3V17H4V3H16V1Z"></path></svg><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="copyButtonSuccessIcon_LjdS"><path fill="currentColor" d="M21,7L9,19L3.5,13.5L4.91,12.09L9,16.17L19.59,5.59L21,7Z"></path></svg></span></button></div></div></div>
</li>
<li>
<p>Configure o repositório remoto e envie o código:</p>
<div class="language-bash codeBlockContainer_Ckt0 theme-code-block" style="--prism-color:#393A34;--prism-background-color:#f6f8fa"><div class="codeBlockContent_biex"><pre tabindex="0" class="prism-code language-bash codeBlock_bY9V thin-scrollbar" style="color:#393A34;background-color:#f6f8fa"><code class="codeBlockLines_e6Vv"><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">git branch -M main</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">git remote add origin git@github.com:seu-usuario/portfolio.git</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">git push -u origin main</span><br></span></code></pre><div class="buttonGroup__atx"><button type="button" aria-label="Copy code to clipboard" title="Copy" class="clean-btn"><span class="copyButtonIcons_eSgA" aria-hidden="true"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="copyButtonIcon_y97N"><path fill="currentColor" d="M19,21H8V7H19M19,5H8A2,2 0 0,0 6,7V21A2,2 0 0,0 8,23H19A2,2 0 0,0 21,21V7A2,2 0 0,0 19,5M16,1H4A2,2 0 0,0 2,3V17H4V3H16V1Z"></path></svg><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="copyButtonSuccessIcon_LjdS"><path fill="currentColor" d="M21,7L9,19L3.5,13.5L4.91,12.09L9,16.17L19.59,5.59L21,7Z"></path></svg></span></button></div></div></div>
</li>
</ol>
<hr>
<h2 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_LWe7" id="step-7-configure-o-docusaurusconfigjs-para-deploy">Step 7: Configure o <code>docusaurus.config.js</code> para Deploy<a href="https://lis-r-barreto.github.io/portfolio/blog/create-portfolio-with-github-pages-and-docusaurus#step-7-configure-o-docusaurusconfigjs-para-deploy" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to step-7-configure-o-docusaurusconfigjs-para-deploy" title="Direct link to step-7-configure-o-docusaurusconfigjs-para-deploy">​</a></h2>
<p>Atualize o arquivo <code>docusaurus.config.js</code> com as configurações de GitHub Pages:</p>
<div class="language-javascript codeBlockContainer_Ckt0 theme-code-block" style="--prism-color:#393A34;--prism-background-color:#f6f8fa"><div class="codeBlockContent_biex"><pre tabindex="0" class="prism-code language-javascript codeBlock_bY9V thin-scrollbar" style="color:#393A34;background-color:#f6f8fa"><code class="codeBlockLines_e6Vv"><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">module</span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">.</span><span class="token property-access">exports</span><span class="token plain"> </span><span class="token operator" style="color:#393A34">=</span><span class="token plain"> </span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">{</span><span class="token plain"></span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">  </span><span class="token literal-property property" style="color:#36acaa">url</span><span class="token operator" style="color:#393A34">:</span><span class="token plain"> </span><span class="token string" style="color:#e3116c">'https://seu-usuario.github.io'</span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">,</span><span class="token plain"></span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">  </span><span class="token literal-property property" style="color:#36acaa">baseUrl</span><span class="token operator" style="color:#393A34">:</span><span class="token plain"> </span><span class="token string" style="color:#e3116c">'/portfolio/'</span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">,</span><span class="token plain"></span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">  </span><span class="token literal-property property" style="color:#36acaa">organizationName</span><span class="token operator" style="color:#393A34">:</span><span class="token plain"> </span><span class="token string" style="color:#e3116c">'seu-usuario'</span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">,</span><span class="token plain"></span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">  </span><span class="token literal-property property" style="color:#36acaa">projectName</span><span class="token operator" style="color:#393A34">:</span><span class="token plain"> </span><span class="token string" style="color:#e3116c">'portfolio'</span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">,</span><span class="token plain"></span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">  </span><span class="token literal-property property" style="color:#36acaa">deploymentBranch</span><span class="token operator" style="color:#393A34">:</span><span class="token plain"> </span><span class="token string" style="color:#e3116c">'gh-pages'</span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">,</span><span class="token plain"></span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain"></span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">}</span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">;</span><br></span></code></pre><div class="buttonGroup__atx"><button type="button" aria-label="Copy code to clipboard" title="Copy" class="clean-btn"><span class="copyButtonIcons_eSgA" aria-hidden="true"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="copyButtonIcon_y97N"><path fill="currentColor" d="M19,21H8V7H19M19,5H8A2,2 0 0,0 6,7V21A2,2 0 0,0 8,23H19A2,2 0 0,0 21,21V7A2,2 0 0,0 19,5M16,1H4A2,2 0 0,0 2,3V17H4V3H16V1Z"></path></svg><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="copyButtonSuccessIcon_LjdS"><path fill="currentColor" d="M21,7L9,19L3.5,13.5L4.91,12.09L9,16.17L19.59,5.59L21,7Z"></path></svg></span></button></div></div></div>
<hr>
<h2 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_LWe7" id="step-8-realize-o-deploy-com-github-pages">Step 8: Realize o Deploy com GitHub Pages<a href="https://lis-r-barreto.github.io/portfolio/blog/create-portfolio-with-github-pages-and-docusaurus#step-8-realize-o-deploy-com-github-pages" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to Step 8: Realize o Deploy com GitHub Pages" title="Direct link to Step 8: Realize o Deploy com GitHub Pages">​</a></h2>
<p>Para construir e publicar seu site, execute:</p>
<div class="language-bash codeBlockContainer_Ckt0 theme-code-block" style="--prism-color:#393A34;--prism-background-color:#f6f8fa"><div class="codeBlockContent_biex"><pre tabindex="0" class="prism-code language-bash codeBlock_bY9V thin-scrollbar" style="color:#393A34;background-color:#f6f8fa"><code class="codeBlockLines_e6Vv"><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">yarn build</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">USE_SSH=true yarn deploy</span><br></span></code></pre><div class="buttonGroup__atx"><button type="button" aria-label="Copy code to clipboard" title="Copy" class="clean-btn"><span class="copyButtonIcons_eSgA" aria-hidden="true"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="copyButtonIcon_y97N"><path fill="currentColor" d="M19,21H8V7H19M19,5H8A2,2 0 0,0 6,7V21A2,2 0 0,0 8,23H19A2,2 0 0,0 21,21V7A2,2 0 0,0 19,5M16,1H4A2,2 0 0,0 2,3V17H4V3H16V1Z"></path></svg><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="copyButtonSuccessIcon_LjdS"><path fill="currentColor" d="M21,7L9,19L3.5,13.5L4.91,12.09L9,16.17L19.59,5.59L21,7Z"></path></svg></span></button></div></div></div>
<p>Isso criará a branch <code>gh-pages</code> e publicará o site em:<br>
<code>https://seu-usuario.github.io/portfolio/</code></p>
<hr>
